description:
Honeycomb Software is an outsourcing development company. The company was founded in March 2015. Members of our team have over 10 years of experience in development. Honeycomb Software specialization is .Net stack.
The company is working with full .Net stack:
Asp.net Core, Asp.net MVC, WebForms;
MS SQL Server, PostgreSQL, MySQL; 
Angular 2+, ReactJS/Redux;
Html/Html5, CSS, JS, jQuery, and other js-frameworks.
